Te3-kun kap I e5 tang5-phoaN7 hou7 he2 sio-si2
Ti7 Ta-khoe u7 chit8-sian e5 Te3-kun lak8-pah-goa7 ni5 ku2,peh-siN3 chin sin3-giong2--e5. Tak8-ni5 chiaN-goeh8 13 jit8 u7 chiong toa7-ku teh ka7 i choe3 siN-jit8 . ChiaN-goeh8 8 jit8 u7 hou7 Thau5-siaN5 e5 lang5 chhiaN2 khi3 sia7-sin5 . In-ui7 lah8-chek-he2 to2 loh8-lai5 , sio-tioh8 Te3-kun e5 saN , soa3 sio seng-khu, long2-chong2 u7 sio 5 sian khi3 ,U7-e5 piN3 he2-hu, u7-e5 sio chit8-poaN3 , u7-e5 sio chhiu2 kap bin7, Chhu3 long2 bo5 sio-tioh8. kau3 thiN-kng khi2-lai5 chiah chai,hit e5 lang5 chin kiaN,kin2 lai5 ka7 Ta-khoe e5 lang5 kong2. Ta-khoe e5 lang5 m7 pang3 i soah,hit e5 lang5 tiaN7-tiaN7 ku3-chai7 lang5 phah, kong2, “Li2 na7 ka7 goa2 phah-si2, goa2 iah8 bo5 thang chhong3 heng5 lin2, che si7 kou-put-chiong e5.” Chit e5 lang5 chhiaN2-sin5 beh kiu5 hok-khi3 , hoan2-tng2 tu2-tioh8 chai-e7 . Koh Te3-kun tu2-tioh8 he2 iah8 boe7 chi2-si7 i, iah8 boe7 chau2; si7 chha5 e5 mih8, oa2-tioh8 he2 chu7-jian5 oe7 sio-khi3. Hian7-si5 chng-nih8 e5 lang5 chin iu-bun7, kong2, phah-sng3 kin-ni5 oe7 chin phaiN2-ni5 tang , sou2-i2 chiah oe7 an2-ni . 
Thian-su beh Kang3-lim5
Ti7 ku7-ni5 ku7-lek8 7 geh8 Gi5-lan5 u7 chit8 e5 he5-siuN7, iau5-gian5 kong2 TiuN Thian-su beh kang3-lim5 , u7 lai5 ka7 i thok-bang7 , kong2 7 , 9 geh8 2 geh8-jit8 e5 tiong-kan , thiN-e7 e5 lang5 beh si2 chit8-poaN3 , u7 in3 kong2-ko3, si3-koe3 po3 lang5 chai . Hit-tiuN kong2-ko3 goa2 pun2-sin u7 khoaN3-kiN3, chiu7-si7 kong2, na7-si7 khoaN3-kiN3 chit-tiuN e5 sian7-su7, a2-si7 ho2-sim e5 lang5 tioh8 kin2-kin2 sia2 7 tiuN po3 lang5 chai , koh tioh8 chiah8 chit8-thiap e5 ioh8-a2. Chit e5 ioh8-hng ti7 kong2-ko3-toaN-lai7 u7 sia2-beng5 , na7 bo5 an2-ni kiaN5 e5 lang5 oe7 thou3 chhiN-huih , poaN3-tiam2-cheng chiu7 oe7 si2 . KhoaN3-kiN3 e5 lang5 chin kiaN ; u7-e5 kin2 khi3 thiah ioh8-a2 ;u7-e5 kin2 sia2 kong2-ko3 po3 lang5 chai . Au7-lai5 hit e5 iau5-gian5 e5 he5-siuN7 u7 hou7 keng2-koaN liah8-khi3 koan2-a2-lai7 khu-liu5 , hit e5 su7 chiah soah . 
Kau2-ong5-kong Thoe3-sin5
 Ti7 nng7 ni5 cheng5 Lo5-tong e5 Bu2-lau2-khiN u7 nng7-e5 chhi7 gu5 gin2-na2 choe3 chit8-sian e5 thou5 ang-a2 , khia5 chit8-chiah-e5 thou5-gu5, chiu7 ka7 i pai3 , au7-lai5 lang5 chiu7 hong-siaN kong2 , chit e5 thou5 ang-a2 oe7 ka7 i khoaN3 gu5, iah8 oe7 liah8 hi5 hou7 i , kong2 na7 u7 pak-tou2-thiaN3 , mng7 i sui5-si5 ho2 . U7 lang5 kong2 , oe7 hou7 khiau-ku oe7 tit8 , chiu7 ka7 i liap-ho7 “Kau2-ong5-kong .” Hut-jian5-kan chit8 jit8 kui2-na7 chheng lang5 khi3 heng5-hiuN hia , khi3 hia sio-kim e5 lang5 , u7 theh8 si3-hang7 tng2-khi3 i-piN7 :--
